
<section>
    <p class="fs-4">Welcome to the med planner. Your one stop for setting up what you need with the right physicians. Here you can find your primary
        physician and specialist. You can make, change, or cancel your appointments. You can also use out appointment tracker to remind you
        of up coming appointments. Use the form below to sign up and just see how easy it all is.
    </p>
</section>

<form class="sign-in p-3">
  <div class="row mb-1">
      <h3>Patient Sign In</h3>
    <label for="email-signIn" class="col-sm-1 col-form-label size fs-5">Email:</label>
    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email-signIn" placeholder="Email Address">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row mb-1">
    <label for="password-signIn" class="col-sm-1 col-form-label fs-5">Password:</label>
    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password-signIn" placeholder="Password">
    </div>
  </div>
  <button type="submit" class="btn sign-in">Sign in</button>
</form>

<form class="sign-up p-3">
